title: Nissan GT-R Track Pack v Porsche 997 Turbo S - /CHRIS HARRIS ON CARS
description: It's been raining in England for the past 6 weeks, so this is a damp test. The GT-R Track Pack seems a bit half-hearted and, on-paper, the 997 Turbo S is the closest rival. I went to an evening track event at Brands Hatch to discover the differences/ work out if the Track pack is worth the extra cash.
tags: NIssan GT-R, Porsche 911 Turbo, Chris Harris
